### Define Step Configuration with Glob Patterns and Dependencies in Pkl

Source: https://github.com/jdx/hk/blob/main/docs/glossary.md

Shows a detailed step configuration in Pkl, including glob patterns for file selection ('glob', 'stage'), commands for checking and fixing code ('check', 'fix'), and a dependency on another step ('depends').

```pkl
steps {
  ["eslint"] {
    glob = List("*.js", "*.ts")
    stage = List("*.js", "*.ts")
    check = "eslint {{files}}"
    fix = "eslint --fix {{files}}"
    depends = List("prettier")  // Run after prettier
  }
}
